 vice president of finance and controller of fritolay international and as a partner with price waterhouse in its audit practice for  years in entertainment advertising and manufacturing areas he was also the strategic planning partner for price waterhouses new york region he worked with pepsico where he served as vice president of business process reengineering for frito lay he has been an independent director of grupo aeromexico sab de cv since  he has been a director of delta air lines inc since february   he served as a director of gol linhas aéreas inteligentes sa from  to may   he served as a director of northwest airlines llc mr bastian is a graduate of st bonaventure university with a bba in  and is also a certified public accountantread full background corporate headquarters po box atlanta georgia united statesphone fax  board members memberships presentceo  directordelta air lines incpresentindependent directorgrupo aeroméxico s a  b de c v education bba st bonaventure university other affiliations northwest airlines llcnwa incacuity brands incnorthwest airlines incst bonaventure universitygol linhas aéreas inteligentes sagrupo aeroméxico s a  b de c v annual compensation salarytotal annual compensation stocks options restricted stock awardsall other compensationexercised optionsexercised options valueexercisable optionsexercisable options valueunexercisable optionsunexercisable options valuetotal value of optionstotal number of options total compensation total annual cash compensationtotal short term compensationother long term compensationtotal calculated compensation request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup competitor compensationnamepos